The '''Marzoon Confederation''' was an alliance of [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] governments. A treaty that admitted the Confederation into the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] was signed onboard the [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrilan]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] [[FarStar|''Freedom's Messenger'']].

